      "title": "100 percent buses will be in service",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Private Bus Owners Association has said that 100 percent of the buses will be in service across the country tomorrow.",
        "Kemunu Wijeratna, president of the association, said that as the schools are planned to be held for 5 days from tomorrow, the association hopes that private bus transport services can be brought to normal."
      ],
